query:
UPDATE nozzleEvaluations 
SET actualThickness = CASE nozzleNumber
  WHEN 'N1' THEN 0.1480
  WHEN 'N2' THEN 0.1350
  WHEN 'N3' THEN 0.1260
  WHEN 'N4' THEN 0.2100
  WHEN 'N5' THEN 0.2740
  WHEN 'N6' THEN 0.2300
  WHEN 'N7' THEN 0.1500
  WHEN 'N8' THEN 0.1390
  WHEN 'N9' THEN 0.5500
END,
updatedAt = NOW()
WHERE inspectionId IN (SELECT id FROM inspections WHERE vesselTagNumber = '57-11-001')
AND nozzleNumber IN ('N1','N2','N3','N4','N5','N6','N7','N8','N9');
